<!doctype html>
<html>
<head>
<meta charset="utf-8">
<title>H38-T005 AI Workflow Map</title>
<style>
  body{font-family:Arial,sans-serif;font-size:11pt;margin:14px;background:#fff;color:#111827}
  table{border-collapse:collapse;width:1280px;table-layout:fixed}
  th,td{border:1px solid #b7c3d0;padding:8px 10px;vertical-align:top;white-space:normal;word-wrap:break-word;line-height:1.35;mso-number-format:"\@"}
  th{background:#dbeafe;font-weight:700;color:#0f172a}.title{background:#1f2937;color:#fff;font-size:16pt;text-align:left;padding:12px}.sub{background:#f8fafc;color:#475569;font-style:italic}.narrow{text-align:center}
</style>
</head>
<body>
<table>
<colgroup><col style="width:115px"><col style="width:190px"><col style="width:230px"><col style="width:240px"><col style="width:165px"><col style="width:220px"><col style="width:120px"></colgroup>
<tr><th class="title" colspan="7">Highway 38 Solutions - H38-T005 AI Workflow Map Sample</th></tr>
<tr><td class="sub" colspan="7">Use this map to turn repeated admin work into intake, sorting, draft, tracking, and handoff steps.</td></tr>
<tr><th>Step</th><th>Input</th><th>Current Issue</th><th>Template or Prompt</th><th>Tracker Field</th><th>Owner Action</th><th>Status</th></tr>
<tr><td>Intake</td><td>Customer request</td><td>Details arrive scattered.</td><td>Missing-info prompt</td><td>Lead status</td><td>Route request to the closest package.</td><td class="narrow">Ready</td></tr>
<tr><td>Sort</td><td>Photos and notes</td><td>Facts are mixed with guesses.</td><td>Sort facts prompt</td><td>Package</td><td>Pick starting package.</td><td class="narrow">Ready</td></tr>
<tr><td>Draft</td><td>Package and scope</td><td>Replies are rewritten every time.</td><td>Quote reply template</td><td>Next action</td><td>Send reply or missing-info note.</td><td class="narrow">Ready</td></tr>
<tr><td>Track</td><td>Status and due date</td><td>Follow-ups are easy to miss.</td><td>Follow-up prompt</td><td>Due date</td><td>Review dashboard.</td><td class="narrow">Ready</td></tr>
<tr><td>Handoff</td><td>Finished output</td><td>Delivery wording changes every job.</td><td>Delivery email prompt</td><td>Delivered date</td><td>Send handoff and upgrade path.</td><td class="narrow">Ready</td></tr>
</table>
</body>
</html>
